For these reasons — close alignment on warm, vocal‑forward mastering, melodic songwriting, and thoughtful sequencing — Revolutions: The Very Best Of Steve Winwood is the better choice for my listening preferences, and the Blues/Slide Guitar compilation is the weaker match.

